{"title_page": "Claudie Cuvelier", "text_new": "{{short description|French athlete}}\n{{Orphan|date=September 2018}}\n\n{{Infobox Athlete\n |name                       = Claudie Cuvelier\n |event                = [[shot put]], [[discus throw]]\n |nationality               = [[France|French]]\n |birth_date         = {{birth-date and age|13 May 1943}}\n |birth_place         = [[Wignehies]]\n}}\n\n'''Claudie Cuvelier''' (married name is '''Schisano)''' (born [[:fr:13 mai en sport|13 May]]   [[1943 in sports|1943]] at [[Wignehies]]) is a former French [[Sport of athletics|athlete]], who specialised in the [[shot put]] and the [[discus throw]].\n\n==  Biography  ==\nShe won three champion of France titles  in the [[shot put]] (1966, 1967 and 1969) and three  champion of France titles in the [[discus throw]] (1967, 1968 and 1969)..\n\nShe three times improved the [[:fr:Record de France du lancer du poids|French shot put record]] (14.58m,  15.11m and 15.31m in 1967) and also she bettered the record three times in [[:fr:Record de France du lancer du disque|the discus]]  (48.54m, 49.70m in 1967, and 50.82m in 1969)\n\n===  Prize list  ===\n* [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme|French Championships in Athletics]]   :  \n** 3 times winner of the shot put in [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1966|1966]],  [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1967|1967]] and [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1969|1969]]   \n** 3 times winner of the discus in [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1967|1967]],  [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1968|1968]] and [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1969|1969]].\n\n=== Records ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\"\n|+'''Personal records'''\n\n! scope=\"col\" |Event\n! scope=\"col\" | Performance\n! scope=\"col\" | Location\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n|-\n|Shot Put\n|15.31 m\n|\n|1967\n|-\n|Discus throw\n|51.02 m\n|\n|1969\n|}\n\n==  References  ==\n*  Docathl\u00e92003, French Athletics Federation, 2003 p.&nbsp;397\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cuvelier, Claudie}}\n[[Category:1943 births]]\n[[Category:French female discus throwers]]\n[[Category:French female shot putters]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Nord (French department)]]\n\n\n{{France-athletics-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|French athlete}}\n{{Orphan|date=September 2018}}\n\n{{Infobox Athlete\n |name                       = Claudie Cuvelier\n |event                = [[shot put]], [[discus throw]]\n |nationality               = [[France|French]]\n |birth_date         = {{birth-date and age|13 May 1943}}\n |birth_place         = [[Wignehies]]\n}}\n\n'''Claudie Cuvelier''' (married name is '''Schisano)''' (born [[:fr:13 mai en sport|13 May]]   [[1943 in sports|1943]] at [[Wignehies]]) is a former French [[Sport of athletics|athlete]], who specialised in the [[shot put]] and the [[discus throw]].\n\n==  Biography  ==\nShe won three champion of France titles  in the [[shot put]] (1966, 1967 and 1969) and three  champion of France titles in the [[discus throw]] (1967, 1968 and 1969)..\n\nShe three times improved the [[:fr:Record de France du lancer du poids|French shot put record]] (14.58m,  15.11m and 15.31m in 1967) and also she bettered the record three times in [[:fr:Record de France du lancer du disque|the discus]]  (48.54m, 49.70m in 1967, and 50.82m in 1969)\n\n===  Prize list  ===\n* [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme|French Championships in Athletics]]   :  \n** 3 times winner of the shot put in [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1966|1966]],  [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1967|1967]] and [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1969|1969]]   \n** 3 times winner of the discus in [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1967|1967]],  [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1968|1968]] and [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1969|1969]].\n\n=== Records ===\n{| border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"2\" class=\"wikitable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\"\n|+'''Personal records'''\n\n! scope=\"col\" |Event\n! scope=\"col\" | Performance\n! scope=\"col\" | Location\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n|-\n|Shot Put\n|15.31 m\n|\n|1967\n|-\n|Discus throw\n|51.02 m\n|\n|1969\n|}\n\n==  References  ==\n*  Docathl\u00e92003, French Athletics Federation, 2003 p.&nbsp;397\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cuvelier, Claudie}}\n[[Category:1943 births]]\n[[Category:French female discus throwers]]\n[[Category:French female shot putters]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Nord (French department)]]\n\n\n{{France-athletics-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "WOSlinker", "label": "safe", "comment": "tidy wikitable options", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claudie_Cuvelier"}
{"title_page": "Carole Sinoquet", "text_new": "{{Orphan|date=August 2016}}\n\n{{Infobox Athlete\n |name                       = Carole Sinoquet\n |event                = [[Hammer Throw]]\n |years_active            = 1990s \n |nationality               = [[France|French]]\n |birth_date         = {{birth-date and age |7 June 1975}}\n |birth_place         = [[Domont]]\n}}\n\n'''Carole Sinoquet''' (born June 7, 1975 at [[Domont]]) is a former French [[Sport of athletics|athlete]], who specialized in the [[hammer throw]].\n\n==  Biography  ==\nShe won two titles of champion of France in the hammer throw in 1995 and 1996.\n\nIn 1996, she improved on four occasions [[:fr:Record de France du lancer du marteau|French hammer throw record]] successively bringing it to 57.06 m,  57.16&nbsp;m,  57.32&nbsp;m and 57.54&nbsp;m.\n\n=== Prize list  ===\n* [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme|French Championships in Athletics]]   :  \n** 2-time winner in the hammer throw [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1995|1995]] and [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1996|1996]].\n\n=== Records ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\"\n|+'''Personal Bests'''\n\n! scope=\"col\" |Event\n! scope=\"col\" | Performance\n! scope=\"col\" | Location\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n|-\n|Hammer throw\n|57.54&nbsp;m\n|\n|1996\n|}\n\n== Notes and references  ==\n* Docathl\u00e92003, F\u00e9d\u00e9ration fran\u00e7aise d'athl\u00e9tisme, 2003, p.&nbsp;432\n\n== External links  ==\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Sinoquet, Carole}}\n[[Category:1975 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:French female hammer throwers]]\n\n\n{{France-athletics-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Orphan|date=August 2016}}\n\n{{Infobox Athlete\n |name                       = Carole Sinoquet\n |event                = [[Hammer Throw]]\n |years_active            = 1990s \n |nationality               = [[France|French]]\n |birth_date         = {{birth-date and age |7 June 1975}}\n |birth_place         = [[Domont]]\n}}\n\n'''Carole Sinoquet''' (born June 7, 1975 at [[Domont]]) is a former French [[Sport of athletics|athlete]], who specialized in the [[hammer throw]].\n\n==  Biography  ==\nShe won two titles of champion of France in the hammer throw in 1995 and 1996.\n\nIn 1996, she improved on four occasions [[:fr:Record de France du lancer du marteau|French hammer throw record]] successively bringing it to 57.06 m,  57.16&nbsp;m,  57.32&nbsp;m and 57.54&nbsp;m.\n\n=== Prize list  ===\n* [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme|French Championships in Athletics]]   :  \n** 2-time winner in the hammer throw [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1995|1995]] and [[:fr:Championnats de France d'athl\u00e9tisme 1996|1996]].\n\n=== Records ===\n{| border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"2\" class=\"wikitable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\"\n|+'''Personal Bests'''\n\n! scope=\"col\" |Event\n! scope=\"col\" | Performance\n! scope=\"col\" | Location\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n|-\n|Hammer throw\n|57.54&nbsp;m\n|\n|1996\n|}\n\n== Notes and references  ==\n* Docathl\u00e92003, F\u00e9d\u00e9ration fran\u00e7aise d'athl\u00e9tisme, 2003, p.&nbsp;432\n\n== External links  ==\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Sinoquet, Carole}}\n[[Category:1975 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:French female hammer throwers]]\n\n\n{{France-athletics-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "WOSlinker", "label": "safe", "comment": "tidy wikitable options", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carole_Sinoquet"}
