ours\" />\n* [[La Liga]]: [[2011\u201312 La Liga|2011\u201312]], [[2016\u201317 La Liga|2016\u201317]]\n* [[Copa del Rey]]: [[2010\u201311 Copa del Rey|2010\u201311]], [[2013\u201314 Copa del Rey|2013\u201314]]\n* [[Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a]]: [[2012 Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a|2012]], [[2017 Supercopa de Espa\u00f1a|2017]]\n* [[UEFA Champions League]]: [[2013\u201314 UEFA Champions League|2013\u201314]], [[2015\u201316 UEFA Champions League|2015\u201316]], [[2016\u201317 UEFA Champions League|2016\u201317]], [[2017\u201318 UEFA Champions League|2017\u201318]]\n* [[UEFA Super Cup]]: [[2014 UEFA Super Cup|2014]],<!--PLEASE DO NOT ADD UEFA SUPER CUP 2016 TO HONOURS. HE WAS NOT PART OF THE SQUAD. SEE \u2192 http://www.uefa.com/uefasupercup/season=2016/clubs/club=50051/squad/index.html. IF YOU DISAGREE, DO NOT ADD, PLEASE DISCUSS ON THE TALK PAGE--> [[2017 UEFA Super Cup|2017]]\n* [[FIFA Club World Cup]]: [[2014 FIFA Club World Cup|2014]], [[2016 FIFA Club World Cup|2016]], [[2017 FIFA Club World Cup|2017]]\n\n'''Juventus'''<ref name=SW />\n* [[Serie A]]: [[2018\u201319 Serie A|2018\u201319]]\n* [[Supercoppa Italiana]]: [[2018 Supercoppa Italiana|2018]]\n\n'''Portugal'''\n* [[UEFA European Championship]]: [[UEFA Euro 2016|2016]]<ref name=\"Euro 2016 final\" />\n* [[UEFA Nations League]]: [[2018\u201319 UEFA Nations League|2018\u201319]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uefa.com/uefanationsleague/news/newsid=2609771.html|title=Cristiano Ronaldo on winning Nations League on home soil|date=9 June 2019|access-date=1 July 2019|website=UEFA.com|publisher=Union of European Football Associations (UEFA)|location=[[Porto]], [[Portugal]]|first=Carlos|last=Machado}}</ref>\n\n'''Individual'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=50em|}}\n<!-- LEAGUE AND FEDERATION-SANCTIONED AWARDS ONLY. No fan or magazine-voted awards. Listed by kind of award. -->\n* [[FIFA Ballon d'Or]]/[[Ballon d'Or]]: [[2008 Ballon d'Or|2008]], [[2013 FIFA Ballon d'Or|2013]], [[2014 FIFA Ballon d'Or|2014]], [[2016 Ballon d'Or|20